Package com.paigegoldhagen.starbower

Interface QueryHandler

All Superinterfaces:
QueryExecutor
All Known Subinterfaces:
ComponentHandler
All Known Implementing Classes:
CheckboxHandler, DatabaseHandler, FestivalComponents, GUI, ScheduleHandler, TimetableHandler, UpcomingEvents
public interface QueryHandler extends QueryExecutor
Interface handling the execution of SQL queries and setting NotifyState, Expansion, Category, Festival, DynamicEvent and Schedule class information.
